r />\n恭喜你<br />\n你條女派左帽比你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地真係真係好睇唔過眼條臭雞黎左一個月就派帽<br />\n因為其中有人見過臭雞既男朋友 斯斯文文咁 仲專登陪佢一齊過黎留幾日先走<br />\n<br />\n佢由12月開始已經成日送上門去人地屋企過夜（最少2日）<br />\n話同個鬼仔好好好岩傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個月起碼要去人地屋企傾幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有邊位巴打想搵我確認下/識得有人資料差唔多 可以留tg<br />\n<br />\n利申：非打手 件事係佢fm爆出黎 我地圍內既人都知 呢幾日聽到佢傾電話先100%確定 有人見過佢男友但唔知點聯絡先上黎開po<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫手推下 <br />\n綠帽唔怕戴 最緊要除得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299612c556fd051a25cd60b92042d39293ca5c3d","tid":995602,"uid":169048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"推上浸大secret 各大銀行secret (如果有) 實睇到啦<br />\n略盡棉力<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"1d021767abcf7147656c83aa2ffdc6d0e5046513","tid":995602,"uid":167426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"如果事主or 事主個fd係CD-ROM咁點睇啊？"},{"pid":"459d11c21fa999bcbcc575f411e3fd0a36b10ab5","tid":995602,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:15:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"36bcbea6fedd140ad60b9dfb2d7912c31ee6e889","tid":995602,"uid":58870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:19:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6baefe27fd2fa5655c287e0404f22a911e6fb3cc","tid":995602,"uid":12818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f48a9bcaa5674bbc83aedeb61f2915fe81e68fdb","tid":995602,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:28:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"092dbfb71ed4b0275535a507f0a98749abbd6390","tid":995602,"uid":10687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci